Entries.default: "Maybe they'll be right back."
"I don't suppose I'd stay here long, either."
"It'd be nice if those Vailians went ahead and disarmed all the traps for us."
"And now we're out of the wind. What else could possibly go wrong?"
"This is slow going."
"I'm never going to get all this out of my shoes."
"Ishi, get in my pack! Too windy here for little birds."
"To shelter, yes? Before my hair dries out."
"So much for misty jungles and crystal beaches."
"We'll be fine, just try not to breathe going through."
"Di verus, at times like this, I'm glad Hylea gave me these eyes."
"Oi, for... Dung-munching gods! There be sand getting up in places I'd forgot I fucking had!"
"Good Gaun! Grit's going to get everywhere."
"Hey, look. Free camp."
"Island life must not have agreed with them."
"This bodes... poorly for my countrymen."
"There be a lesson to learn here about mercantile types and hostile environs - one that ends with us taking their stuff."
"This looks down right hospitable... for an abandoned campsite."
"Dust off your feathers, Ishi. I don't like this."
"Sand has encroached in all the wrong places, I say."
"I be smelling the booty from here, cap. ...and I'll be over here practicing my phrasing."
"I'm all right! A tad windblown but no worse for the wear."
"Don't go near that thing, Ishiza. Hurts my head just looking at it..."
"Ugh. The tentacle rots from the base up, I say."
"Tell me you don't plan on... connecting with this pillar."
"Think I found the problem."
"Ain't never seen poxy adra afore, cap. Ain't never got this queer feeling in my head, neither."
"Looking at that thing's enough to make me queasy. For the love of Gaun, don't touch it."
"This drags on worse than Kana's poetry."
"For this I left the guild?"
"There sometimes be advantages to standing short of a barstool. This ain't one of them times."
"It's like moving through molasses, ain't it?"
